<br>
1. Mob cannot be rooted<br>
2. Mob cannot be 'chasing' anyone.<br>
3. Has a long reuse time on the disc (72 minutes?)<br>
4. As mentioned, if the mob sticks its toenail into a wall, the ranger will do about 20% of his potential damage.<br>
5. People get in the way.<br>
6. Have to either spend a TON of time and money making the arrows, or a TON of time maxing AA skills.<br>
7. Need the top end bows.<br>
8. Very limited number of targets this is useful (practical) on.<br>
<br>
<br>
...9, they can do 2100 dmg in one hit.<br>
<br>
This is not overpowered in the least. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=milaru>Milaru</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer<BR>Don't mind me,<BR>it's the PMS talking!</span><br>  Posts: 1570<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/18/02 3:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: +26000 damage to CT via a BOW???</span><hr size=1> Grim, I was referring to whoever said they solo better than us.  Although fearkiting CT would be something for the books.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uxuraz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Xuraz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 31<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/18/02 3:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: re:</span><hr size=1> Against Dragons, Aren't Wizards able to do comperable damage with their AA abilities + Dragonbane?  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
